//                'practice_area_type' => 'personal_injuries',
//                'banner_image' => 'storage/practice_areas/insurance_badfaith_banner.webp',
//                'content_image' => 'storage/practice_areas/insurance_badfaith.webp',
//                'short_description' => '<div><span style="color: rgb(109, 109, 109); font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(249, 248, 246, 0.48); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;">We trust insurance companies to respect us when we bring a legitimate claim. They owe their policyholders a duty of good faith and fair dealing. When that trust is broken, whether it be from an auto claim, a home claim, a medical claim, a life insurance claim, we know how to get you on a level playing field and make them pay for being unfair and taking advantage of you, their insured.</span></div>',
//                'description' => '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 33px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgba(249, 248, 246, 0.48); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;">Insurance companies sell policies to their policyholders to help them through difficult times, to protect them against financial disaster when a fire occurs, or an earthquake, or an unexpected accident on your property, or a car crash happens. You depend on your insurance to be there. But insurance companies often fail to put their insured’s situation into proper focus, and instead work too hard to protect their own assets. And that’s not fair. In fact, it’s illegal..</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 33px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgba(249, 248, 246, 0.48); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;">When insurance companies fail to live up to the terms of their policies and unreasonably delay or deny payment of valid claims, people come to us, and we try to make them pay as they promised. We’ve fought for grieving widows, for proper medical care, for fair compensation arising from various unexpected events where insurance should have covered the issue. And we looking forward to helping you.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgba(249, 248, 246, 0.48); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;padding: 0px 33px">Here are some facts regarding bad faith cases in the U.S-<a href="https://www.mondaq.com/unitedstates/insurance-laws-and-products/763918/negligent-bad-faith-limiting-insurance-bad-faith-to-its-roots" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(196, 163, 75);">Click here</a></p>',
//                'created_at' => date('2021-08-12 H:i:s'),
//                'updated_at' => date('2021-08-12 H:i:s'),
//            ],
//            [
//                'slug' => 'mass-transit-incidents',
//                'title' => 'Mass Transit Incidents',
