                'practice_area_type' => 'civil_rigits',
                'banner_image' => 'storage/practice_areas/police_brutality_banner.webp',
                'content_image' => 'storage/practice_areas/police_brutality.webp',
                'short_description' => '<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_1  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_light" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px !important; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 29.6719px; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 7px !important; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 52px !important; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 33px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: center center / cover no-repeat rgba(249, 248, 246, 0.48); overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: left; animation-timing-function: linear; animation-duration: 200ms; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(196, 163, 75) !important; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><div class="et_pb_text_inner" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 33px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; position: relative;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 33px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">CIVIL RIGHTS</p></div></div><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_2 et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_text_align_justified-tablet et_pb_bg_layout_light et_multi_view__hover_selector et_multi_view__hovered" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 40px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 49px !important; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: center center / cover no-repeat rgba(249, 248, 246, 0.48); overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: left; animation-timing-function: linear; animation-duration: 200ms; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; color: rgb(109, 109, 109) !important; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><div class="et_pb_text_inner" data-et-multi-view="{&quot;schema&quot;:{&quot;content&quot;:{&quot;desktop&quot;:&quot;<p>The heart of the Cochran Firm lies in civil rights law, civil rights litigation, civil rights trials, and making this a better and more just society through enforcement of our Constitutionally guaranteed civil rights. We are police brutality lawyers, helping families in Los Angeles and throughout California.<\/p>\n<p>The most common civil rights cases we take involve people who are <strong>wrongfully shot<\/strong> <strong>and seriously injured or killed by the police<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Have you been:\u00a0<\/strong><br \/>Wrongfully harassed?<br \/>TASED by the police?<br \/>Beaten by the police?<\/p>\n<p>Time matters. Get in touch with us today!<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>We can help you! <a href=\&quot;https:\/\/cochranfirmlaw.com\/contact-us\/\&quot; style=\&quot;color: #c4a34b;\&quot;>Contact us here<\/a><\/p>&quot;,&quot;tablet&quot;:&quot;<p>The heart of the Cochran Firm lies in civil rights law, civil rights litigation, civil rights trials, and making this a better and more just society through enforcement of our Constitutionally guaranteed civil rights. We are police brutality lawyers, helping families in Los Angeles and throughout California.<\/p>\n<p>The most common civil rights cases we take involve people who are wrongfully shot and seriously injured or killed by the police. Some of the people we have fought for were wrongfully harassed, TASED, or beaten by the police.<\/p>\n<p>We can help you! <a href=\&quot;https:\/\/cochranfirmlaw.com\/contact-us\/\&quot; style=\&quot;color:#c4a34b\&quot;>Contact us here<\/a><\/p>&quot;}},&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;et_pb_text&quot;}" data-et-multi-view-load-tablet-hidden="true" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; position: relative;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 33px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">The heart of the Cochran Firm lies in civil rights law, civil rights litigation, civil rights trials, and making this a better and more just society through enforcement of our Constitutionally guaranteed civil rights. We are police brutality lawyers, helping families in Los Angeles and throughout California.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 33px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">The most common civil rights cases we take involve people who are<span>&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">wrongfully shot</strong><span>&nbsp;</span><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">and seriously injured or killed by the police</strong>.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 33px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; font-weight: bold;">Have you been:&nbsp;</strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;">Wrongfully harassed?<br style="box-sizing: border-box;">TASED by the police?<br style="box-sizing: border-box;">Beaten by the police?</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 33px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">Time matters. Get in touch with us today!</p></div></div>',
                'description' => '<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_3 et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_text_align_center-phone et_pb_bg_layout_light et_multi_view__hover_selector" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 29.6719px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px !important; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px !important; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: center center / cover no-repeat rgba(249, 248, 246, 0.48); overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: left; animation-timing-function: linear; animation-duration: 200ms; font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><div class="et_pb_text_inner" data-et-multi-view="{&quot;schema&quot;:{&quot;content&quot;:{&quot;desktop&quot;:&quot;<p style=\&quot;text-align: justify;\&quot;>We are the leaders in civil rights law in California, and have been known for this commitment by the community we serve, law enforcement, and their lawyers. We have earned the respect of the bar and bench in this area. Our Managing Partner, Brian Dunn, specializes in such cases and is known to be Los Angeles’ best and most effective civil rights trial lawyer.<\/p>\n<p style=\&quot;text-align: justify;\&quot;>Here is a helpful Police Violence Report for 2021\u00a0 –<span style=\&quot;color: #c4a34b;\&quot;><a href=\&quot;https:\/\/policeviolencereport.org\/\&quot; style=\&quot;color: #c4a34b;\&quot;> Click here<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\&quot;text-align: justify;\&quot;>Who polices the police? The Cochran Firm. We know that our police are so often heroes. We understand that every day they go to work they lay their lives on the line for each of us. We believe that they must make snap decisions, life or death decisions, under stress and rapidly evolving situations. Nonetheless, their power is awesome. We, as a society, delegate to the police the right to use force against us, and in some cases, the right to use lethal force against us, the citizens, the people who live, work, and enjoy life, liberty and the pursuit of happiness here.<\/p>\n<p style=\&quot;text-align: justify;\&quot;>Here are some examples of Civil Rights violations by the police \u2013 <a href=\&quot;https:\/\/www.justice.gov\/crt\/law-enforcement-misconduct\&quot; style=\&quot;color: #c4a34b;\&quot;>Click here<\/a><\/p>\n<p style=\&quot;text-align: justify;\&quot;>There is a balance which must be struck between the awesome and deadly power the police are entrusted with and their need to protect and serve the community and not overreact or emotionally choose to cause harm out of proportion to the threat they have before them, in our society. The Cochran Firm, through its work, enforces that proper balance.<\/p>\n<p style=\&quot;text-align: justify;\&quot;>If you are looking for Police Brutality Lawyers in Los Angeles, we probably take more civil rights cases to trial than any other firm. We take the most significant cases involving police misconduct.<\/p>&quot;,&quot;tablet&quot;:&quot;<p style=\&quot;text-align: justify;\&quot;>We are the leaders in civil rights law in California, and have been known for this commitment by the community we serve, law enforcement, and their lawyers. We have earned the respect of the bar and bench in this area. Our Managing Partner, Brian Dunn specializes in such cases and is known to be California finest civil rights trial lawyer.<\/p>\n<p style=\&quot;text-align: justify;\&quot;>Who polices the police? The Cochran Firm. We know that our police are so often heroes. We understand that every day they go to work they lay their lives on the line for each of us. We believe that they must make snap decisions, life or death decisions, under stress and rapidly evolving situations. Nonetheless, their power is awesome. We, as a society, delegate to the police the right to use force against us, and in some cases, the right to use lethal force against us, the citizens, the people who live, work, and enjoy life, liberty and the pursuit of happiness here.<\/p>\n<p style=\&quot;text-align: justify;\&quot;>Here are some examples of Civil Rights violations by the police \u2013 Click here<\/p>\n<p style=\&quot;text-align: justify;\&quot;>There is a balance which must be struck between the awesome and deadly power the police are entrusted with and their need to protect and serve the community and not overreact or emotionally choose to cause harm out of proportion to the threat they have before them, in our society. The Cochran Firm, through its work, enforces that proper balance.<\/p>\n<p style=\&quot;text-align: justify;\&quot;>If you are looking for Police Brutality Lawyers in Los Angeles, we probably take more civil rights cases to trial than any other firm, and our commitment is significant. If we cannot help you, we will make sure someone else who believeas we do how vital civil rights cases are will help. We take the most significant cases involving police misconduct.<\/p>&quot;}},&quot;slug&quot;:&quot;et_pb_text&quot;}" data-et-multi-view-load-tablet-hidden="true" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; position: relative;"><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 33px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify;">We are the leaders in civil rights law in California, and have been known for this commitment by the community we serve, law enforcement, and their lawyers. We have earned the respect of the bar and bench in this area. Our Managing Partner, Brian Dunn, specializes in such cases and is known to be Los Angeles’ best and most effective civil rights trial lawyer.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 33px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify;">Here is a helpful Police Violence Report for 2021&nbsp; –<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; color: rgb(196, 163, 75);"><a href="https://policeviolencereport.org/" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(196, 163, 75);"><span>&nbsp;</span>Click here</a></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 33px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify;">Who polices the police? The Cochran Firm. We know that our police are so often heroes. We understand that every day they go to work they lay their lives on the line for each of us. We believe that they must make snap decisions, life or death decisions, under stress and rapidly evolving situations. Nonetheless, their power is awesome. We, as a society, delegate to the police the right to use force against us, and in some cases, the right to use lethal force against us, the citizens, the people who live, work, and enjoy life, liberty and the pursuit of happiness here.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 33px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify;">Here are some examples of Civil Rights violations by the police –<span>&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.justice.gov/crt/law-enforcement-misconduct" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(196, 163, 75);">Click here</a></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 33px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify;">There is a balance which must be struck between the awesome and deadly power the police are entrusted with and their need to protect and serve the community and not overreact or emotionally choose to cause harm out of proportion to the threat they have before them, in our society. The Cochran Firm, through its work, enforces that proper balance.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-align: justify;">If you are looking for Police Brutality Lawyers in Los Angeles, we probably take more civil rights cases to trial than any other firm. We take the most significant cases involving police misconduct.</p></div></div><div class="et_pb_button_module_wrapper et_pb_button_1_wrapper  et_pb_module " style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: center center / cover no-repeat rgba(249, 248, 246, 0.48); animation-timing-function: linear; animation-duration: 200ms; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;"><a class="et_pb_button et_pb_button_1 et_pb_bg_layout_light" href="sms:+18336763254" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0.3em 1em; border: 2px solid rgb(158, 125, 50); outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: center center / cover no-repeat transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important; font-weight: 500; position: relative; border-radius: 3px; transition: all 300ms ease 0ms; line-height: 1.7em !important; display: inline-block;">Text "LegalHelp" to 833-676-3269</a></div>',
