//                'practice_area_type' => 'personal_injuries',
//                'banner_image' => 'storage/practice_areas/spinal_cord_injury_banner.webp',
//                'content_image' => 'storage/practice_areas/spinal_cord_injury.webp',
//                'short_description' => '<div><span style="color: rgb(109, 109, 109); font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgba(249, 248, 246, 0.48); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; display: inline !important; float: none;">The Spinal Cord Injury&nbsp; well-protected within the body, but when it is damaged, paralysis can occur.With Spinal Cord Injuries a rapid decline in health can happen, and very complex and costly medical attention is required. We have&nbsp; great experience with spinal cord injury survivors, and look forward to assisting those who suffer with such an injury.</span></div>',
//                'description' => '<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 33px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgba(249, 248, 246, 0.48); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;">Our focus with spinal cord injury cases is assessing where the money to care for the needs of spinal cord injury survivors will come from. If we can hold those responsible for the injury to pay for the care needed, then a very comprehensive assessment and life care plan is needed. We work with a team of experts on such cases, including neurologists, neurosurgeons, physiatrists and rehabilitation medicine specialists, physical therapists, occupational therapists, psychologists, psychiatrists, vocational experts and ultimately economists, to put the lifetime damages into present-day perspective.</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 33px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgba(249, 248, 246, 0.48); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;">Here are some facts regarding spinal cord injuries in the U.S-<span>&nbsp;</span><a href="https://journals.lww.com/ajpmr/FullText/2017/02001/People_with_Spinal_Cord_Injury_in_the_United.27.aspx" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(196, 163, 75);">Click here</a></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; text-size-adjust: 100%; vertical-align: baseline; background: rgba(249, 248, 246, 0.48); color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Montserrat, Helvetica, Arial, Lucida, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: justify;padding: 0px 33px">We realize that spinal cord injury survivors need to focus their attention on their health and adjusting to any new physical or psychological changes in their lives. We help make sure you get the best experts, the prompt attention, and ensure, if the case is one we can get appropriate economic justice from, your lifetime needs are in place.</p>',
